Flicker/Skyblaze/Phoenix::

"Save your hostility for when it's needed, Starstorm."  Flicker leads 
the group inside to the mess hall and plunks himself down at a 
table.  Skyblaze sits across from him, and Phoenix goes to fetch the 
group some refreshments.  "Now, we're going to talk about this 
reasonably.  Aerotaur, if you're really on our side, then you'll have 
to problem talking about the current tactical situation at the 
Maximal base - as best you know it, of course."
